Invocation Name: ab workout
des:
A simple and effective high-intensity ab circuit to strengthen and tone your core. 

This 5 Minute Ab Workout has five sets of 1 minute ab exercises with 30 second rests between sets. Start by doing just one round a day -- and build up to two or three!

Circuit:
1 min - Crunches
1 min - Sculler sit-ups
1 min - Toe touches
1 min - Bicycles
1 min - Double leg lifts
*30 second rest between sets
